'''Weet-Bix'''&trade;
===Proper Noun===
# a [[biscuit]] of compressed wholegrain flakes. "Australia's favourite breakfast for the whole family". A national food icon of Australia.
===Derived Terms===
#'''had one's Weet-Bix today'''. Applied to a person [[exhibit|exhibiting]] plenty of [[vitality]] or [[strength]] or other superior [[performance]].
